                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-12 mt-4">
                                    <h2 class="font-weight-bold">
                                        About Us
                                    </h2>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Klyde is a new direct-to-market premium furniture brand. Each Klyde is crafted
                                        from
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>the highest-grade materials, making for a genuine
                                        quality and lasting experience
                                        of
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        luxury.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Klyde is the antidote to fast furniture, a rejection of disposable furniture.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Our range is a combination of on-trend pieces along with totally innovative
                                        smart
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        designs by our head designer, focusing on solving specific interior problems.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Klyde are designed to stimulate, evoke a mood and above all - Nurture.
                                    </p>
                                    <p/>
                                    <hr/>
                                    <p class="about_p" style="line-height: 2;">
                                        Designed in Sydney Australia
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Crafted from high-grade materials
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Sold directly to market
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                    </p>
                                    <hr/>
                                    <h4>
                                        Designer Focused
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        The mission of Klyde is to enable design creators to realise their visions, to
                                        facilitate
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        product design development and to enable authentic craftmanship to deliver
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        on the creator’s promise. Digital visualization tools and a unique real-time
                                        quoting
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        service provide an easy workflow and rapid self-service experience.
                                    </p>
                                    <h4>
                                        Quality
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Our direct-to-market model enables us to invest more into the quality of
                                        materials
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        and product construction. Klyde is more than attractive furniture, quality and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        craftsmanship is a core principle of our brand.
                                    </p>
                                    <h4>
                                        Earth Care
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        The world does not need another high street furniture store.
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Klyde is built from a digital footprint, offering a smarter delivery platform
                                        from a
                                        smaller carbon footprint.
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Our first goal was to be 100% free of polystyrene. With the use of honeycomb
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        cardboard internal packaging we have said goodbye to the hideous and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        ubiquitous polystyrene foam.
                                    </p>
