                                        Earth Care
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        The world does not need another high street furniture store.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Klyde is built from a digital footprint, offering a smarter delivery platform
                                        from a
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        smaller carbon footprint.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Our first goal was to be 100% free of polystyrene. With the use of honeycomb
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        cardboard internal packaging we have said goodbye to the hideous and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        ubiquitous polystyrene foam.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        We are now actively working on our upstream supply chain to develop sustainable
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        materials. It is not a quick fix but Klyde’s commitment is to invest more energy
                                        and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        resources into the quality and sustainability of materials.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="mt-5">
                        <div class="container-fluid">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 text-right">
                                    <img src="/vixo_add_to_quotation/static/src/img/team3.jpg" class="img img-fluid"
                                         style="width: 200px;height: 200px;"/>
                                    <h4>
                                        Brian Qi
                                    </h4>
                                    <p>
                                        Head of Design
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                                    <h4>
                                        Meet Our Designer
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Brian Qi is a multidisciplinary designer based in Sydney, formally trained with
                                        a
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Bachelor Degree of Architecture and Master’s Degree in Design, he has worked
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        in the commercial design industry for 10 years on both interior architecture and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        furniture design projects.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Brian has won several design awards including the prestigious Red Dot Design
                                        Award
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        in 2018, with his work included in the collection of the Red Dot Design Museum
                                        in
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        China.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="about_p">
                                        Brian’s design philosophy centres around problem-identifying and
                                        problem-solving.
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        Always looking for new ways with which to use materials, finishes and innovative
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        manufacturing processes to deliver something unique.
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        We are now actively working on our upstream supply chain to develop sustainable
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        materials. It is not a quick fix but Klyde’s commitment is to invest more energy
                                        and
                                        <br class="d-none d-md-block"/>
                                        resources into the quality and sustainability of materials.
                                    </p>
